://IP/phpinfo.php |</div>\r\n<div>| Prober: http://IP/p.php |</div>\r\n<div>+------------------------------------------------------------------------+</div>\r\n<div>| Add VirtualHost: lnmp vhost add |</div>\r\n<div>+------------------------------------------------------------------------+</div>\r\n<div>| Default directory: /home/wwwroot/default |</div>', 'LNMP状态管理命令', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-28 11:40:38', '2016-11-28 03:40:38', '', 41, 'http://luchanglong.com.cn/?p=42', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
