unix</a>版本不一样，所以部分语法有差别，例如在hp unix aix 中设定间隔执行如果采用*/n 方式将出现语法错误，在这<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%B1%BBunix\" target=\"_blank\">类unix</a>中 ，间隔执行只能以列举方式。</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">实例《添加一个每分钟执行脚本一次的定时任务》：</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">1.创建要执行的文件 ，记得更改权限</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"># vi /root/do.sh</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"> 写入要执行的命令</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">2.创建任务</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"># crontab -e</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">在编辑页面中写入</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">* * * * * /root/do.sh</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">保存，查看当前任务</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"># crontab -l</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\">任务设置成功！</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\"></div>', 'linux 使用crontab 做定时任务', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '287-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 14:49:31', '2017-03-17 06:49:31', '', 287, 'http://luchanglong.com.cn/?p=290', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES (292, 1, '2017-03-17 17:13:46', '2017-03-17 09:13:46', '# chown root  Application/Runtime/   修改所有者\r\n# chmod -R 777 Application/Runtime/    修改权限（文件夹递归）', 'linux 修改文件权限和修改用户', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '285-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-17 17:13:46', '2017-03-17 09:13:46', '', 285, 'http://luchanglong.com.cn/?p=292', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES (293, 1, '2017-03-18 11:24:22', '2017-03-18 03:24:22', '解锁\r\n\r\nsvn unlock /home/www/jjhome\r\n\r\n检出\r\n\r\nsvn checkout svn://120.xx.xx.xx/jjhome  jjhome\r\n\r\n更新\r\n\r\nsvn update\r\n\r\n批量提交修改\r\n\r\n输入命令：$svn st  查看状态 ，状态M表示修改\r\n\r\n输入命令：$svn st | grep \"M\" | cut -c 8-&gt;modified.txt  将修改存入modified.txt文件\r\n\r\n输入命令：svn ci -m \"add files\" --targets modified.txt 将修改递交到SVN服务器\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n用 svn info &lt;Item&gt; 命令查询，其中&lt;Item&gt;是要查询的文件，得到最近提交的Revision编号，例如\r\n\r\n# <strong>svn info src/main.cpp</strong>\r\n\r\n得到的结果中有这样一行：<strong>Last Changed Rev: 25114</strong>\r\n\r\n然后用 svn diff -c &lt;Revision&gt; &lt;Item&gt;，即\r\n\r\n# <strong>svn diff -c 25114 src/main.cpp</strong>\r\n\r\n就能查询到最近一次提交的改动', 'svn 命令更新和提交修改', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'svn-%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0%e5%92%8c%e6%8f%90%e4%ba%a4%e4%bf%ae%e6%94%b9', '', '', '2017-03-18 14:08:52', '2017-03-18 06:08:52', '', 0, 'http://luchanglong.com.cn/?p=293', 0, 'post', '', 269);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES (294, 1, '2017-03-18 11:24:22', '2017-03-18 03:24:22', '解锁\r\n\r\nsvn unlock /home/www/jjhome\r\n\r\n检出\r\n\r\nsvn checkout svn://120.xx.xx.xx/jjhome  jjhome\r\n\r\n更新\r\n\r\nsvn update\r\n\r\n批量提交修改\r\n\r\n输入命令：$svn st  查看状态 ，状态M表示修改\r\n\r\n输入命令：$svn st | grep \"M\" | cut -c 8-&gt;modified.txt  将修改存入modified.txt文件\r\n\r\n输入命令：svn ci -m \"add files\" --targets modified.txt 将修改递交到SVN服务器\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'svn 命令更新和提交修改', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '293-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-18 11:24:22', '2017-03-18 03:24:22', '', 293, 'http://luchanglong.com.cn/?p=294', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES (295, 1, '2017-03-18 11:28:09', '2017-03-18 03:28:09', '解锁\n\nsvn unlock /home/www/jjhome\n\n检出\n\nsvn checkout svn://120.xx.xx.xx/jjhome  jjhome\n\n更新\n\nsvn update\n\n批量提交修改\n\n输入命令：$svn st  查看状态 ，状态M表示修改\n\n输入命令：$svn st | grep \"M\" | cut -c 8-&gt;modified.txt  将修改存入modified.txt文件\n\n输入命令：svn ci -m \"add files\" --targets modified.txt 将修改递交到SVN服务器\n\n&nbsp;\n\n用 svn info &lt;Item&gt; 命令查询，其中&lt;Item&gt;是要查询的文件，得到最近提交的Revision编号，例如\n\n# <strong>svn info src/main.cpp</strong>\n\n得到的结果中有这样一行：<strong>Last Changed Rev: 25114</strong>\n\n然后用 svn diff -c &lt;Revision&gt; &lt;Item&gt;，即\n\n# <strong>svn diff -c 25114 src/main.cpp</strong>\n\n就能查询到最近一次提交的改动', 'svn 命令更新和提交修改', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '293-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-18 11:28:09', '2017-03-18 03:28:09', '', 293, 'http://luchanglong.com.cn/?p=295', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
